title: Friday Night Pints (with Brandon Walker, Kayce Smith, Ellie Schnitt, Jared Carrabis, Robbie & Trent)
description:
Debuting last Friday, Friday Night Pints is a happy hour we streamed live on Twitter, Youtube and Barstoolsports.com featuring the Barstool talent scattered around due to the Coronavirus quarantine. With Brandon Walker, Kayce, Jared, Ellie, Robbie & Trent joining KFC & Feits. We will do it again next Friday, for catch it live then.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
